					expression="_this setVariable ['Description',_value,true];";
					class Value
					{
						class data
						{
							singleType="STRING";
							value="In the tumultuous nation of Mutambara, Extremist insurgents are wreaking havoc by targeting helpless civilians, escalating an already dire situation. Entrusted with the responsibility, the Mutambara Security Forces, an elite and resolute unit, prepare to quell the insurgent uprising and safeguard the lives of innocent inhabitants.<br/><br/>Amidst the chaos, the Security Forces find themselves engaged in fierce battles, meticulously strategizing and suppressing the imminent threat posed by the insurgents. However, the looming mission holds a significant weight â€“ to repel the insurgents' forthcoming attack on the vulnerable village of Mwami. With the clock ticking, the Security Forces mobilize, poised to fiercely defend Mwami and its inhabitants.<br/><br/>Should they succeed in thwarting the enemy's relentless advance and emerging victorious, the Security Forces will capitalize on the gained momentum. Swiftly transitioning to a calculated counter-offensive, they will strike at the core positions of the insurgent forces within the expansive area of operations.<br/><br/>This pivotal moment will determine the fate of the region, as the Security Forces' unwavering dedication and unyielding resolve will be put to the test. With each step forward, they inch closer to reclaiming stability and ensuring the well-being of the oppressed population.";
						};
					};
				};
