							value="1. Mortars will fire flares to mark their strike areas. Flares indicate that you need to take cover<br/>" \n "2. Resupply can be found at the HQ in Mwami for the counter-attack.<br/>" \n "3. Extra AT and Grenades can be found in boxes around the trenches.<br/>" \n "4. Counter-battery duties will be very important to avoid destruction of the entire village. This is a priority tasking, mortars need to be active for phase 1.<br/>" \n "5. Flares for grenadiers are located in their backpacks. Switch out your handgun to use.";
